      <title>比利时央行行长续任因政治僵局暂缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/belgium-central-bank-chief-renewal-on-hold-over-political-deadlock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比利时国家银行行长的任期尚未续任，这可能导致该央行明年初失去领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/belgium-central-bank-chief-renewal-on-hold-over-political-deadlock</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 12:33:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙延长缓解通胀措施的期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/spain-extends-some-measures-put-in-place-to-ease-inflation-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管上个月通胀有所缓和，但西班牙仍延长了政府为保护家庭免受生活成本飙升影响而实施的一些措施，包括降低食品税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/spain-extends-some-measures-put-in-place-to-ease-inflation-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 12:33:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
